results.title: Young X-Men (2008 - 2009)
results.description: Being a teenager? Tough. Being a mutant? Really tough. If you're both? Life won't be easy. YOUNG X-MEN follows the adventures of the next generation of X-Men as they train, learn and try to survive in a very difficult world. If you're looking for teenage angst in the Mighty Marvel Manner with a healthy dose of mutant shenanigans, this is the book for you.
